data.title: Time Publishing And Media Co.,Ltd. Company Profile - China
data.text: With owned publishing, printing and other cultural media asset and by subscribed Keda Innovation directed shares, Anhui Publishing Group has become the largest shareholder of listed companies. It is the first culture and media company went to public by offering its entire publishing business and has become the listed company with highest return on net asset, high potential grow and great investment value. The company is mainly engaged in publishing, media, printing and reproduction, high-tech R&D and transfer of scientific and technological achievements. It also focuses on high-tech of electronics and information engineering and application, information and communication technology, information control technology and other electronic information product development and promotion.
